<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: The Anomaly -->
  <TheAnomaly.label>异常现象</TheAnomaly.label>
  <!-- EN: Your research expedition has finally arrived at the source of the anomalous signal: an ancient archotech monolith on a distant planet. As you survey the structure from orbit, the scanner's audio feed forms garbled syllables which repeat your own name over and over. Your crewmate screams as her flesh begins flowing and reforming. A blinding beam of energy reaches up from the planet and tears your research vessel apart. You have disturbed something ancient and inhuman.\n\nNote: This is a difficult scenario and is not recommended for new players. -->
  <TheAnomaly.description>你的研究探险队终于到达了异常信号的源头：一个遥远星球上的远古超凡科技巨石。当你们在轨道上勘察这座建筑时，扫描仪的音频信号形成了杂乱的音节，一遍又一遍地重复着你自己的名字。你的船员尖叫起来，她的血肉开始流动和重组。一道耀眼的能量光束从行星上射来，将你的研究飞船撕成碎片。你惊扰了一些远古非人的惊惧之物。\n\n注意：该剧本十分困难，不建议新玩家尝试。</TheAnomaly.description>
  <!-- EN: Your research expedition has finally arrived at the source of the anomalous signal: an ancient archotech monolith on a distant planet. As you survey the structure from orbit, the scanner's audio feed forms garbled syllables which repeat your own name over and over. Your crewmate screams as her flesh begins flowing and reforming. A blinding beam of energy reaches up from the planet and tears your research vessel apart. You have disturbed something ancient and inhuman.\n\nNote: This is a difficult scenario and is not recommended for new players. -->
  <TheAnomaly.scenario.description>你的研究探险队终于到达了异常信号的源头：一个遥远星球上的远古超凡科技巨石。当你们在轨道上勘察这座建筑时，扫描仪的音频信号形成了杂乱的音节，一遍又一遍地重复着你自己的名字。你的船员尖叫起来，她的血肉开始流动和重组。一道耀眼的能量光束从行星上射来，将你的研究飞船撕成碎片。你惊扰了一些远古非人的惊惧之物。\n\n注意：该剧本十分困难，不建议新玩家尝试。</TheAnomaly.scenario.description>
  <!-- EN: The Anomaly -->
  <TheAnomaly.scenario.name>异常现象</TheAnomaly.scenario.name>
  <!-- EN: The ancient monolith unleashed an energy pulse that tore your research vessel apart and mutated your crew. Only a few of you made it to the escape pods.\n\nDespite the setback, your mission is far from over. If you can learn more about the monolith, perhaps you can find a way to shut it down - or harness its inhuman power. -->
  <TheAnomaly.scenario.parts.GameStartDialog.text>这块古老的巨石释放出的能量脉冲将你们的研究船撕成碎片，并使船员发生异变。\n\n尽管遭受打击，但你们的任务远未结束。如果你们能对巨石有更多的了解，也许就能找到关闭它的方法——抑或者将这股超凡的力量化为己用。</TheAnomaly.scenario.parts.GameStartDialog.text>
  <!-- EN: Start with one ghoul and two colonists. -->
  <TheAnomaly.scenario.parts.ConfigurePawnsMutants.customSummary>以一个食尸鬼和两名殖民者开始游戏。</TheAnomaly.scenario.parts.ConfigurePawnsMutants.customSummary>
  <!-- EN: Two researchers and a ghoul investigate an ancient monolith. -->
  <TheAnomaly.scenario.summary>两名研究人员和一个食尸鬼调查了一块古老的巨石。</TheAnomaly.scenario.summary>
  
</LanguageData>